{"tid":1791593,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［星二代］小S女兒出道被力棒為時尚新秀","createTime":"2019-12-21T03:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T10:01:18.000Z","uid":215823,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"409ae3518c30395fa3a3dd60e165d9e769926413","tid":1791593,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0dJNdfM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0dJNdfM.jpg&h=2ba5a6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifRfm87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifRfm87.jpg&h=8ffaeeb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iA4ft8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iA4ft8.jpg&h=828b8950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小 S 徐熙娣的 13 歲大女兒 Elly 許曦文今年 9 月為時尚品牌 JORYA 拍攝一系列時尚大片，遺傳到媽媽的完美基因，Elly 天生修長高挑的身材加上「高級厭世臉」整個人散發出名模氣場，讓網友超驚艷！當媽的小 S 當時也不忘力挺女兒分享她的美照，卻搞笑寫下「在家如果敢擺這個表情給我看，一腳就飛踢過去！」讓網友快笑到爛！而今天 JORYA 就又曝光了一組 Elly 的全新時尚大片，比起上一次，Elly 在鏡頭下變得更有自信、也更有個性美了！不只這樣，小Ｓ 也再次親自下海教女兒怎麼用眼神放電，再度引爆話題！"},{"pid":"367c1c5e25e182a46539d2143c975050e8fe106f","tid":1791593,"uid":215823,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"小S則轉發女兒系列作品照，並寫下：「<span style=\"color: red;\">她臉雖高級</span>，但本人很幼稚！」字裡行間藏不住以女兒為榮的驕傲，但又不改小S的搞怪個性，而品牌也有釋出小S親到攝影棚指導Elly的影片，對此，小S則寫下：「世上只有媽媽好，有媽的孩子像個寶～」。"},{"pid":"04142f764fda780354cdd6fdfa9b4875a828386e","tid":1791593,"uid":35538,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"迪士尼應該搵佢拍 Mulan"},{"pid":"d958d58ee089905d27363b1d1891afa259d94cfa","tid":1791593,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:44:21.000Z","msg":"...嚇親 me"},{"pid":"20a94e293f49570d33cc6fef8bb32a347214be34","tid":1791593,"uid":1067,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/